Liked “Hi Abby! Hailey here with Ullrich Insurance Agency! Just wanted to give you a quick update. As suspected, it was a timing issue - the $186.99 refund has already been initiated and will be back in your account 11.21.2025 per Travelers billing. 

Let me know if you have any further questions! I hope you have a wonderful rest of your day!”
